(In reply to robi from comment #14) > I already reported this bug: > https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1299145 Months ago, nobody ever > seemed to notice, can somebody please take a look at this? I have this bug > multiple times a day it's driving me mad.
So you have no ideas on how to reproduce this issue but expect me to fix it, that's never going to happen. Cinnamon runs fine here and for everyone else (your the only one reporting this issue), so the issue is with your setup. Try removing all user added thirdparty applets, desklets and extensions and see if the issue is still there. If that fails try creating another user account and see if that has the issue.
